Defendant Masharee Chardell Delane not in court, in custody.  Paul Leonard Tiffin in court, appeared in person for State of Wisconsin.

No use or possession of controlled substances without a valid prescription, no drug paraphernalia. Defendant advised it is a requirement to attend all future court proceedings. Failure to comply with conditions of bail may result in an additional charge of bail jumping.

Defendant Masharee Chardell Delane in court with attorney Nicholas John Conrardy.  Defendant Masharee Chardell Delane in custody.  Kelly O'Neill appeared for the State of Wisconsin.
